{
  "title": "Testing and Optimizing Your Content",
  "html": "<main><header class=\"section-page-header\"><div class=\"row d-flex justify-content-between\"><div class=\"col col-sm-10\"></div><!----></div><!----><h1>Testing and Optimizing Your Content</h1><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\"> How to make sure your content does what you expect it to, at the quality and frame rates that you need. </p><!----></header><!----><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-9 print-w-100\"><div class=\"b-img\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Testing and Optimizing Your Content\" width=\"1920\" height=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" decoding=\"auto\" ng-img=\"true\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/e9c1cc7f-56c2-4a8c-a3c5-52110371637c?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/e9c1cc7f-56c2-4a8c-a3c5-52110371637c?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335 1x, https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/e9c1cc7f-56c2-4a8c-a3c5-52110371637c?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=3840&amp;height=670 2x\"></div><!----><!----><!----><header class=\"document-header mb-3 d-lg-none d-print-none\"><content-nav class=\"content-nav is-collapsible\" ngh=\"6\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></content-nav></header><!----><article><!----><!----><div document-content-blocks-renderer=\"\" class=\"d-block\" ngh=\"10\"><div id=\"content-blocks-renderer\" class=\"content-blocks-renderer\"><block-switch-control class=\"block-switch-control\" ngh=\"7\"><!----></block-switch-control><block-switch-info class=\"block-switch-info\" ngh=\"8\"><!----></block-switch-info><blocks-renderer id=\"blocks-renderer\" ngh=\"9\"><!----><block-markdown ngh=\"2\"><div class=\"block-markdown\"><p><strong>Unreal Engine</strong> includes tools and features that help developers test and optimize content for applications that need to run at framerates for high-quality experiences.</p>\n\n<p>To learn more, read about the following topics.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"topics\">Topics</h2>\n\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Tool that enables analyzing realtime gameplay data at runtime.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:using-the-gameplay-debugger-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Gameplay Debugger\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/e37a8db7-01eb-4d3e-94c5-04306a10b56d/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"An introduction to using Oodle compression solutions in Unreal Engine.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:using-oodle-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Using Oodle\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/743a1286-51fc-42a5-a7a6-af32fe6a2359/oodle-topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"View and modify all console variables used in your project using the Console Variables Editor, and share console variable settings in a preset across projects.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:console-variables-editor\" page-name=\"Console Variables Editor\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/91d44247-3f11-4a63-a07b-8f1c39ab67e7/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Learn about crash reports and how to use the Crash Reporter in your projects.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:crash-reporting-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Crash Reporting\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/87941aea-5e97-4bd3-bcc2-7eec3219c719/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Record the GPU states for your application in advance to optimize rendering.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:optimizing-rendering-with-pso-caches-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"PSO Caches\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/40416f3d-94c4-433a-b8e4-663a33bd2270/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Adjust performance in project-specific ways with the Significance Manager\" href=\"#unreal-doc:significance-manager-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Significance Manager\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/626eddec-b81f-410c-a7eb-dae22e434dfe/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Console commands specific to displaying game statistics\" href=\"#unreal-doc:stat-commands-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Stat Commands\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/7c67beac-f13f-4011-baf0-d84de1ca37d3/statcommand_topicimage.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Profile your project's performance with Unreal Insights.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:unreal-insights-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Unreal Insights\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/b6bb65f0-31be-40d7-8592-c8e0dedb4909/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"An Overview of Unreal Engine 5's runtime loader.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:zen-loader-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Zen Loader\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/2d3e2096-823f-45e5-9807-6ffb302f6d2b/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"The Stats System collects and displays performance data to help optimize Unreal Engine projects\" href=\"#unreal-doc:unreal-engine-stats-system-overview\" page-name=\"Stats System Overview\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/facf8642-057c-43cb-b22a-d0b0dc30a570/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Framework for lightweight, module-centric tests.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:low-level-tests-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Low-Level Tests\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/626da82d-4c82-4213-bb93-071c297fae81/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Tool that captures state from actors and then displays it visually in game or editor.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:visual-logger-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Visual Logger\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/d9bc15aa-b0c0-4359-9835-c26ed6ff7729/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Instrument Clang sanitizers in your builds for Android and Linux to quickly diagnose problems.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:using-clang-sanitizers-in-unreal-engine-projects\" page-name=\"Clang Sanitizers\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/1eb475a2-0664-43e8-ade5-ed380f93b713/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n<block-dir-item-md description=\"Overview of the automation system used for unit testing, feature testing, and content stress testing.\" href=\"#unreal-doc:automation-test-framework-in-unreal-engine\" page-name=\"Automation Test Framework\" topic-image=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/fc36aab6-0e2f-4b86-b00a-cdbdd0971be0/placeholder_topic.png\" type=\"topic\"></block-dir-item-md>\n</div></block-markdown><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></blocks-renderer></div><!----></div></article><!----><div class=\"col-lg-3 d-none d-lg-block d-print-none\"><!----></div></div><!----><!----><!----></main>",
